 Risks & Mitigation Strategies
Risk	Impact	Mitigation
Breaking UI Changes	Layouts may shift due to grid updates	Perform thorough UI testing before deployment
JavaScript Errors	jQuery-based scripts will break	Refactor to vanilla JS or use Bootstrap 5 native JavaScript
CSS Conflicts	Removed/renamed classes may cause styling issues	Update custom styles and use new Bootstrap utilities
Plugin Compatibility	Third-party libraries relying on Bootstrap 4 may break	Verify compatibility and upgrade dependencies
